             was indicted for <rs id="t17641017-17-off92" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17641017-17-off92" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17641017-17-off92" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing 86 pieces of leather, cut for heels of shoes, value 10 s. and 53 pieces of leather, cut for soles of shoes, value 30 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17641017-17-victim204" type="victimName">
                     Daniel 
                     Waldron 
                  <interp inst="t17641017-17-victim204" type="surname" value="Waldron"></interp>
