                  </persName>
            . I have known William the son upwards of two years; he is exceedingly good and honest. I have trusted him to receive and pay money for me, above a thousand pounds value.</p>
               <p>Q. What are you?</p>
               <p>Graham. I am clerk to Messrs. Fuller and Cope, bankers; but this was on my own account.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17641017-17-person224">
                  Samuel 
                  Collier 
               <interp inst="t17641017-17-person224" type="surname" value="Collier"></interp>
